data.description: Introducing a timeless Craftsman-style Cape Cod residence that embodies both classic charm and modern convenience. This meticulously crafted 3 bedrooms & 2 1/2 bathroom home is a true gem in the heart of Wythe. Step inside and be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors that seamlessly guide you through the spacious, light-filled rooms. The well-designed layout boasts not one, but two primary bedrooms, one on each floor. The semi-open concept design creates a welcoming flow between the living spaces, allowing for easy entertaining. Natural light pours in through numerous windows, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere throughout. This property offers a generous backyard and a detached garage that provides ample space for parking and storage. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Contact us today for a private viewing!
